        <span class="stacked">
            <img class="righted" src="<%= asset_path 'blog2_2.png' %>" width="350" height="186" style="padding: 15px;" alt="pololu valley" />
            <p>Something about travel comforts and inspires. Maybe it's the change in scenery. New people and new words. The excitement of finding adventure everywhere. Exploration is built into human DNA. There's nothing quite like cycling down a steep mountain with nothing but the ocean and wind in front of you.</p>
            <p>This place is definitely rubbing off. The designs we've come up with are uniquely inspired by the landscape and the wonderful people. An artist probably can't help being influenced by their environment. There's a sense here that the new band must be as energetic and pure as the lava, the mountains, the rolling ocean. </p>                    
